Package src.music

Class Song

java.lang.Object
src.music.Song
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Song extends Object implements Serializable
The Song class represents a song. It contains data such as the genre, title, artist, album, and number of votes for the song. This class follows encapsulation principles.
